        <h1>Reading from a File</h1>
        <p>Use the <code>fread()</code> function to read data from a file.</p>
        <pre><code>FILE *file = fopen("example.txt", "r");
if (file != NULL) {
    char buffer[255];
    fread(buffer, sizeof(char), sizeof(buffer), file);
    printf("Data read from file: %s\n", buffer);
    fclose(file);
}</code></pre>
